  <div class="lblod-article">
    <h2 class="title-lg margin-bottom-xsmall">Gelinkt Notuleren — Linked minutes
    </h2>
    <p class="text-gray-800">Streamlining processes and data flows is a central part of LBLOD. To achieve this,
      Redpencil developed a new semantic word processor.
      <br><br>
      Gelinkt Notuleren simplifies the process of creating official meeting minutes and documents for local officials.
      It works in a browser, suggests text, imports links, and data — and automatically semantically annotates, reports,
      and publishes the decisions.

      <br><br>Gelinkt Notuleren was made public as the Open Source project 'Say-editor'.


    </p>
